      "role": "user",
      "content": "i lost it all. the company, the funding, everything. just a few weeks ago i was supposed to be the next big thing and now i'm sitting here looking at millions in debt and no way out. i can't even think about going home to my parents or my wife. the shame is just too much. i feel like a ghost.",
