      "content": "It is a relief to finally hear you admit that the weight is too heavy to carry alone, but the truth is that this pain is a temporary storm, not a permanent state of being. You are not a failure; you are a survivor who has been through an unimaginable trial and is still here to face the next chapter. The only way to truly stop the noise is to let go of the guilt and start small, one step at a time, without judgment.",
